<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About Me</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #d6e8f9;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    .about-section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .card-custom {
      border: 3px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease;
      animation: pulseBorder 3s infinite;
    }

    .card-custom:hover {
      border-color: #0d6efd;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.2);
    }

    .card-img-top {
      width: 100%;
      height: 350px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    @keyframes pulseBorder {
      0% {
        border-color: #0d6efd;
      }
      50% {
        border-color: #6610f2;
      }
      100% {
        border-color: #0d6efd;
      }
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #0d6efd;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container about-section">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-md-5 text-center animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
        <div class="card card-custom shadow">
          <img src="/myImage.jpg" alt="My Photo" class="card-img-top" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7 animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Hello, I'm <span class="highlight">Peter</span></h2>
        <p>
          I'm a passionate <span class="highlight">IT Specialist</span> and educator who loves teaching young minds how to code and create with technology. I currently work with Ocatad Engineering Limited and specialize in HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, Alice 3, and more.
        </p>
        <p>
          When Iâ€™m not building or teaching, I enjoy exploring new tech tools, refining my design skills, and learning how AI can improve education. I'm also deeply passionate about making digital learning accessible and fun for students across Nigeria.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
